      "raw_text": "At the special meeting of the city\ncouncil tonight the Washington Water\nPower company's franchise for Hang\nman creek bridge will come up before\nthe committee of the whole. So Will\nthe proposition of General Tannatts\nson to overlook the plans of City En-\ngineer Gill and Fossil Weymouth.\n\n\nTwo big fights are on and there is\na possibility that Gill will 60 down\nto defeat on thereservoir and water\nproposition, and that the generals ;\nson will be installed by the republican\nmajority.\n\n\nThe committee consideration of the\nbridge franchise may develop another\nraid on the treasury of the Washing\nton Water Power company."
